{"tid":1663774,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"真係望唔透 望唔清究竟P牌仲有乜意義","createTime":"2019-10-19T15:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T15:49:28.000Z","uid":431,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d6b2d6eec162aac667aae619c5457a9cf0d2a4a5","tid":1663774,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T15:28:56.000Z","msg":"P牌已經好冇癮<br />\n評分唔准推文唔得<br />\n一日先畀出得嗰一個PO<br />\n成日要珍而重之噉就住出<br />\n好喇等足廿四小時畀出PO喇<br />\n諗住見有啲嘢幾有意思<br />\n落足心機撚到靚靚同大家分享<br />\n一句不推文就「得」落嚟<br />\n分享老香港嘅好就話人打飛機<br />\n唔知以前點好點光復以前噉呀？<br />\n唔啱睇咪唔睇唔評上一頁囉<br />\n專登叫人唔好睇算咩意思？<br />\n真係世事已經畀你看透了呀？<br />\n識唔識諗吓其他人感受？<br />\nP牌呢個制度已經有問題<br />\n搞到非P牌好似特權階級噉<br />\nP牌就同CD-ROM冇乜分別<br />\n一日P牌就好似一世P牌<br />\n某啲人一見P牌就覺得唔使理<br />\n一係就覺得P牌一定係五毛<br />\n仲要代表P牌話P牌唔介意<br />\n噉即係自己上咗岸得啦？<br />\n後生上唔到岸關人隱士呀？<br />\nP牌顧全大局幾多人顧P牌呀？<br />\n咁怕五毛封晒五毛IP帳號好冇？<br />\n淨係留非P牌喺度夠啦係咪？<br />\n仲畀新會然申請帳號做乜？<br />\n就算封晒五毛IP帳號禁申請<br />\n有專制就會有五毛搵辦法喺度<br />\n十個PO有九個PO總有個負評<br />\n非P牌就完全係黃冇五毛咩？<br />\n行動PO有幾多上熱門呀？<br />\n有幾多P牌嘅PO上熱門吖？<br />\n預咗P牌開PO等沉底<br />\n手足中槍PO都得少數手足推<br />\n噉都唔使落井下石吓話？<br />\n一向唔會點批評自己友<br />\n而家真係唔點醒啲人唔得<br />\n真係唔知開個帳號嚟有乜謂<br />\n再係噉真係聽玩完㗎喇<br />\n都係蒜狗掃帚啦<br />\n怕且都係等睇變潮文<br />\n或者呢個就係P牌嘅意義<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a623c3542a59c74385f059506e0169c4f2c28cdf","tid":1663774,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T15:29:05.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1284ad03264939d98a16c4280412370914a488f1","tid":1663774,"uid":431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T15:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ad5d9ee11a2fb74607ad7002eaadb2ca62ed3b","tid":1663774,"uid":206337,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T15:29:24.000Z","msg":"樓主五毛 拉"},{"pid":"0a8cd857239d07dee7b4cea04fbd7dc5ce219be5","tid":1663774,"uid":23758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T15:29:59.000Z","msg":"衰鬼計多端"},{"pid":"beeec31cef0d92a4cb19cd65e09b5ca28ceeafe7","tid":1663774,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30ad5d9ee11a2fb74607ad7002eaadb2ca62ed3b","tid":1663774,"uid":206337,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T15:29:24.000Z","msg":"樓主五毛 拉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T15:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57eb678657b2a7ad4da58a8937f50a6f5624d00f","tid":1663774,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike